organic.title: Gynecologic Cancers - Willamette Valley Cancer Institute
organic.snippet: The five main types of gynecologic cancers are cervical, ovarian, uterine, vaginal, and vulvar. Learn about these cancers in order to reduce your risks.

organic.title: Willamette Valley Cancer Institute in Eugene, Oregon
organic.snippet: Eugene Cancer Center is at 520 Country Club Road, Eugene, OR 97401. Phone: 541-683-5001. Hours: Mon-Thu 7:30am-6:30pm, Fri 7:30am-6pm. Pharmacy hours are also listed.

organic.title: Willamette Valley Cancer Institute - Providence Directory
organic.snippet: Willamette Valley Cancer Institute offers Oncology, Gynecologic, and Hematology services. Located at 3355 Riverbend Dr Ste 240, Springfield, OR. Call 541-683-5001.

organic.title: Willamette Valley Medical Center
organic.snippet: Willamette Valley Medical Center (WVMC), established in 1904, is a 60-bed acute care facility offering services like emergency, surgery, and behavioral health. Chat with us to find a provider.
